import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'

const MyRouter = () => {
  return (
   <Router>

    <Routes>
       <Route>
        <Route path="/" element={<Layout />}/>
       </Route>
    </Routes>
   </Router>
  )
}

export default MyRouter
